{"type":"visualization","id":"logs-explore-discover-guide","attributes":{"title":"Open Discover for field sidebar","description":"Managed by shared-gitops-k8s-cluster","visState":"{\"title\":\"Open Discover for field sidebar\",\"type\":\"markdown\",\"params\":{\"fontSize\":12,\"openLinksInNewTab\":false,\"markdown\":\"## Use Discover for filters (Logz.io-style left panel)\\n\\n[**Open Logs / Signal**](/app/data-explorer/discover/#/?_g=(filters:!(),refreshInterval:(pause:!f,value:30000),time:(from:now-15m,to:now))&_a=(discover:(columns:!(resource.attributes.k8s@namespace@name,serviceName,observedTimestamp,severityText,log.attributes.event_class,log.attributes.event_category,log.attributes.method,log.attributes.path,log.attributes.status,log.attributes.duration_ms,log.attributes.has_trace,body),interval:auto,sort:!(!(observedTimestamp,desc))),metadata:(indexPattern:shared-observability-logs,view:discover))&_q=(filters:!(),query:(language:lucene,query:'log.attributes.event_class%3Aapplication'))) \\u2014 default triage.\\n[**Open Logs / HTTP**](/app/data-explorer/discover/#/?_g=(filters:!(),refreshInterval:(pause:!f,value:30000),time:(from:now-15m,to:now))&_a=(discover:(columns:!(resource.attributes.k8s@namespace@name,serviceName,observedTimestamp,severityText,log.attributes.event_class,log.attributes.event_category,log.attributes.method,log.attributes.path,log.attributes.status,log.attributes.duration_ms,log.attributes.has_trace,body),interval:auto,sort:!(!(observedTimestamp,desc))),metadata:(indexPattern:shared-observability-logs,view:discover))&_q=(filters:!(),query:(language:lucene,query:'log.attributes.event_class%3Aapplication%20AND%20log.attributes.event_category%3Ahttp'))) \\u2014 access logs (`Request completed` / method \\u00b7 path \\u00b7 status \\u00b7 duration).\\n\\n### Filter order\\n1. **namespace** (`loadlinker` / `sesame-idam` / `rerp`)\\n2. **application** (`serviceName`)\\n3. **time** (picker, top right)\\n4. **event_category** (`http` / `auth`) or